try, and Short paper camera-ready papers due (Extended to May 20) May 2, 2016 Author registration deadline for Research, Industry, and Short papers (Extended to May 20) May 16, 2016 Poster, Doctoral Symposium, Workshop and camera-ready papers due (Extended to May 27) May 16, 2016 Author registration deadline for Posters, Doctoral Symposium, and Workshops (PARIS, GSE-Ed), (Extended to May 27) www.icgse.org HOME | CFP | DATES | PROGRAM | REGISTRATION | COMMITTEES | SPONSORSHIP | VENUE | PUBLICITY | VISITORS INFORMATION | NEWS | CONTACT | PREVIOUS Please forward usability issues to webmaster, Andrea Stockl | deastockl@gmail.com